Title: The Dinner Party
Plot: The gang struggles to find gifts for a dinner party. Jerry and Elaine stop at a bakery to get a cake, but they forget to take a number and lose the chocolate pastry and the one they get has a hair on it. Kramer and George try to get the wine but must get change for a $100 dollar bill and wait for a double-parker to return to his car.
GuestStars: Fred Pinkard, Frank Novak, Mark Holton, Suzy Soro, Kathryn Kates, S. Marc Jordan, Langdon Bensing, Sayed Badreya, Amjad J. Oaisen, Roger Eschbacher
